{"tid":1947153,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam client webhelper 食好多ram","createTime":"2020-03-28T06:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T03:35:44.000Z","uid":33510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3f449d5e194d7d320f795389850a33c32c4671","tid":1947153,"uid":33510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkuR89S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkuR89S.jpg&h=75c05177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如題, 一開steam 乜都開唔到, store library page 都load 唔到<br />\nSteam client webhelper 可以食到20gb ram<br />\n試過:<br />\nDelete download cache<br />\nDelete web browser cache<br />\nReinstall steam<br />\nReboot pc<br />\n<br />\n奇怪係我用另一個windows user login 我個steam account 又乜事都冇<br />\n有冇人遇過同樣情況同點解決? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb6b17d99892738ba4af6fc8e9c869f7066db64","tid":1947153,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"因為係用electron 寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e433a7ad42b851d834c90df70ab1ece2227cb19","tid":1947153,"uid":256957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG8jySa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG8jySa.jpg&h=9860745b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aef0ba1599d6abd08013ee61370c802c971c03cc","tid":1947153,"uid":6677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e433a7ad42b851d834c90df70ab1ece2227cb19","tid":1947153,"uid":256957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG8jySa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG8jySa.jp